Will you have the HBCU’s designs in store for Black History Month?

Thanks for your inquiry regarding our Black History Month collection. Each year, Target partners with HBCU students to submit designs for Target's Celebration of Black History Month. Winners and finalists receive prizes, mentoring opportunities and a chance for their art to appear in-store and on https://tgt.biz/7fb0b0. This year will be no different. We will include designs from Target's HBCU Design Challenge winners to the collection as usual. Happy shopping and have a great day!
